   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Ten HE WHO BELIEVES HAS ETERNAL LIFE Scripture: John 3:36 Eternal life The eternal life is not just a blessing, but even more, it is another life.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The eternal life is a life that is eternal.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>It is God s life.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Only God s life is an unlimited life, a powerful, holy, bright, loving, and righteous life.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Man s life Man s original life is a fragile life.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Being hit by a car or taking a little too much tranquilizer will immediately terminate it.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>It is also a limited life.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Men live fifty, sixty, eighty, or even one hundred years and die.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>The life span is limited and life soon vanishes away.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Man s life is also evil and is destined to die.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Speak on sin and death.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Items I and II are the comparisons of God s life with man s life.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>How to obtain eternal life The eternal life is in God s Son.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>It is the life of God.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>In order to have the eternal life men must have the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>The Son of God is God and is also the Spirit.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>In order to have Him men must receive Him with their spirit, that is, believe in Him.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>After receiving Him with their spirit, after believing in Him, men will have the eternal life.</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>As the Scripture says, he who believes in the Son has eternal life.</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>The consequence of not believing Men who do not believe will not have eternal life because the eternal life is in God s Son.</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>If you do not believe, you will not have eternal life.</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>If you do not believe, the wrath of God is upon you.</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>The eternal life is in the Son of God, while the wrath is according to God s righteousness.</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>If you believe in the Son of God, you will have eternal life.</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>If you do not believe in the Son of God, you will remain under the wrath of God.</S>
   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>God s wrath is like the thunder ready to roll.</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>When it rolls, men will perish.</S>
   </TEXT>
